name: SmartDishwasher
0:
”Alexa, ask Smart Dishwasher what state the dishwasher is in”
”Alexa, tell Smart Dishwasher to set the dishes to be clean.”
”Alexa, tell Smart Dishwasher to set the dishes to be dirty.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: smart dishwasher
des: Tell Smart Dishwasher whether the dishes are clean and it will remember for the next person! Great to keep dirty dishes from mixing with clean dishes in your house.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
